description:
Some of us have experienced anxiety throughout the lockdown. Peter, in the Bible, also struggled with anxiety and self-doubt which can make him relatable to us now.

Jesus let Peter have his humbling experiences because He knew Peter would need to learn from the storm. Like us, Peter was a work in progress. If God has the power to do amazing things like removing Peter’s self-doubt, He can do it for us! 

More than 2 billion people worldwide believe in the Bible and God’s power to change lives for the better.  Just like the story of Peter, all we have to do is to have an unwavering confidence in Jesus. Whenever we are frightened, pray to our Almighty Savior.
